description.Name: description
description.Value: 80km Desert Ride, endurance ride in 2002 with over 100 starters. I came in 21st with an average speed of 14km per hour with a horse I loaned and trained myself, this was our first season and we were still learning, the winners averaged over 22 km per hour so I was really pleased with the performance.
